{"type": "article", "id": 27110, "title": "Old Navy 将关闭日本全部门店，以及，科比推出限量腕表｜浮华日报", "description": "我们为你挑选了今天最重要和最好看的时尚新闻。\r\n", "date": "2016-05-20T11:40:20Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 3593, "name": "户外"}, {"id": 341, "name": "运动"}, {"id": 3735, "name": "德国"}, {"id": 11728, "name": "关店"}, {"id": 50, "name": "日本"}, {"id": 141, "name": "展览"}, {"id": 1705, "name": "腕表"}, {"id": 11592, "name": "夏季"}, {"id": 27915, "name": "大衣"}, {"id": 2326, "name": "Gap"}, {"id": 27, "name": "Nike"}, {"id": 27916, "name": "Hublot"}, {"id": 992, "name": "Chanel"}, {"id": 25410, "name": "PVH"}, {"id": 27917, "name": "AXO"}, {"id": 27421, "name": "Beams"}, {"id": 6674, "name": "ACG"}, {"id": 3078, "name": "Max Mara"}, {"id": 26138, "name": "Kobe Bryant"}, {"id": 19699, "name": "Gabrielle Chanel"}], "category": 19, "column": 8, "author": 113313, "comment_count": 3, "praise_count": 32, "image": "img/article/article_show/2016070213293154UOj1azNCFM6v0c.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<h2>一些重要的新闻：</h2>\n<p><a href=\"http://m.us.fashionmag.com/news/Gap-to-close-75-Old-Navy-Banana-Republic-stores-outside-North-America,694831.html\"><b>Gap 集团海外市场将关闭 75 家门店</b></a>｜Gap 集团继发布一季度财报，其净收入下跌了 46.8% 后，近日宣布将在海外市场关闭 75 家 Old Navy 和 Banana Republic 的门店，将重心移回北美市场以求品牌复苏。其中日本的 Old Navy （53 家）门店将全部关闭。截止 4 月 30 日，Gap 集团在北美有 1029 家 Old Navy，在亚洲有 69 家。同时北美拥有 607 家 Banana Republic，亚洲及欧洲地区有 61 家。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/markets-news/ready-to-wear-sportswear/pvh-corp-grupo-axo-forge-mexican-joint-venture-10433960/\"><b>PVH 集团与 Axo 集团成立合资企业，进军墨西哥</b></a>｜PVH 集团与墨西哥 Axo 集团周四宣布达成建立合资企业的协议，以在墨西哥运营及管理 PVH 旗下所有品牌（包括 Calvin Klein、 Tommy Hilfiger 和 Warner’s 等）的分销。过去，Axo 集团已经在墨西哥负责 Tommy Hilfiger  品牌的生意长达 22 年，Axo 也与 LVMH 旗下的丝芙兰成立合资公司进军墨西哥。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/fashion-news/fashion-scoops/chanel-culture-exhibition-venice-10433807/\"><b>Chanel Culture 展将在威尼斯开幕</b></a>｜坐落于威尼斯的佩萨罗宫现代艺术画廊(Ca’Pesaro International Gallery) 将举办 “The Woman Who Reads” 的主题展览，香奈儿 Culture 展览作为其中的一部分，将展示 Chanel 创始人 Gabrielle Chanel 与书和阅读之间的联系，展览将从 9 月 17 日持续至次年的 1 月 8 日。而 Culture Chanel 展览由 Jean-Louis Froment 构想、策划，开始于 2007 年的莫斯科，随后的城市包括上海、北京、巴黎、首尔等。</p>\n<p class=\"\"><a href=\"https://hypebeast.com/2016/5/kobe-bryant-hublot-classic-fusion-herovillain\"><b>宇舶表推出科比限量腕表</b></a>｜Kobe Bryant 再次与瑞士顶级钟表品牌宇舶表（Hublot）合作，推出一个新的限量系列，名为“Classic Fusion Kobe Bryant HeroVillain”。黑金主色调，可以看到黑色蛇形的镶嵌，致敬科比的“黑曼巴”代号。此系列腕表只限量发行 24 块，其中包括科比自己佩戴的编号为 24 的一块。2013 年成为 Hublot 形象大使后，Kobe 曾与其合作推出过两款腕表。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<p></p>\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702132916kSx24pOuCzgHT8ts.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702132916q20lIYpJQdz8jusf.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702132916acyfIig9uL5rvNnH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66759259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2>一些值得一看的：</h2>\n<p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://bae.hypebeast.com/2016/5/cara-delevingne-suicide-squad-w-magazine\">Cara Delevingne 为 <i>W </i>杂志拍摄封面</a>：<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<p></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702132917UKcWJYa3tIFN7oE6.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702132917QSEMtcd2near4X7u.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"placeholder\"></figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702132918Y7IJt5XrDTZahqfL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702132919UP4L9XAT1eFr6S8Z.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021329197MgZ1vmwJcV26TUP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://www.fashiongonerogue.com/max-mara-atelier-fall-2016/\">Max Mara 已推出秋冬大衣系列</a>，羊驼、粗花呢、马海毛和羊绒材质的长款大衣为主：</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<p></p>\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702132920T0i3GZNWa8pvdPQ6.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66111111\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702132921DdWXy2SoFPe9mjx4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66111111\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702132921ApfzLtk0QvEeliBX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66111111\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702132921Euh7MsK3t06ZdoOy.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66111111\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702132922kR7CQDqS6c5fm0A4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66111111\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\">一向代表摇滚精神的 Dr. Martens 近日与日本百货 Beams 推出合作鞋款，三孔的漆皮鞋男女皆可，女款可把附赠的丝带系成蝴蝶结，看起来挺少女。此前我们报道过 Beams 为庆祝成立 40 周年<a href=\"http://www.qdaily.com/articles/26622.html\">在新宿三丁目新开了东京旗舰店</a>。6 月 25 日在日本发售。</p>\n<p class=\"multiple\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702132922fkCrD0ztFgSTqJxB.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702132923HlBT1LwqQOWJEfKZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702132923KoRnW1NLxAU4jDw3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702132924HJtNMs6imlfq7U3R.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702132924T0Q7AglMxmabhYwc.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<p class=\"\">Nike ACG  即 NikeLab 旗下高端户外机能品牌（全天候装备）推出了<a href=\"http://hypebeast.com/2016/5/nikelab-acg-2016-summer-lookbook\"> 2016 夏季新品</a>，由德国著名户外品牌 ACRONYM 创始人  Errolson Hugh 设计：</p>\n<p class=\"multiple\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702132924cknua2CQXzWH6obt.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702132925e7sxXThnOc4SGogL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702132925OUecxH3R6Adh59Dn.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702132926uVKbc8SZXP4ylCpi.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021329264qyDfmeh3JS6N97i.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702132926JIYFVPC0kKLe9f8l.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<p class=\"\">H&amp;M 又发布了<a href=\"http://www.fashiongonerogue.com/hm-summer-beach-looks-2016/\">新的夏季潮流指南</a>，这次是关于沙滩上怎么穿：</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<p></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021329276pzyt8jlU1D7adJ4.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702132929XiyqjsEfAkgMTLap.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702132929jKsf8LqFWJbQ0cCA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702132929DjBUd5I94Ky70fkl.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021329300n9iwQ36qmHX7TIO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\"><br></p>\n\n"}